{
  "stem": "23626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He used to say to bring him that glove.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he would be in the back yard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he told me to stay there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he put that big glove on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He trained those dogs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think this was the time when I was called for to testify against Goeth in Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And somehow, when I was telling this story, and I was talking about the dogs, all of the sudden, [SOBBING] I-- this scene came in front of me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[CRYING] [SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I blacked out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I-- I really couldn't talk anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I just seeing how he would stay and give this order to the-- especially the the Ralf.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He would say, Ralf!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the dog would run and tear people apart-- but tear 'em apart, would grab by parts of the body.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he would be standing there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I mean, I don't think I can ever forget it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] [SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] [SOBBING] He hated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was full of hate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Sometimes I remember this one particular time, when I was-- you know, he had a mistress living with him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He-- he lived the most luxurious life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He had a beautiful villa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There were weekly and daily delivery of fresh meat, fresh cold cuts, fresh fruit, fresh vegetables, wine, liquor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He had his mistress.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Her name was Ruth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She lived with him there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And he had his two slaves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I was one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SOBBING] And this one day, when Ruth went to Krakow, to town-- which she frequently did go, in a closed up carriage, black carriage.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And she would bring all kinds of things that she bought.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "She brought flowers.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
